name: CoreAPI Run_Tile
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Run_Tile Details
about:
Description

Planet 9-Run_Tile manages the list of the planet 9 Application tiles and the corresponding applications.

API Run_Tile is the API to access the Planet 9 application tiles, and the operations performed on tiles.

You can use API Run_Tile into your app to add, delete, or update the tile content. 

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the API Run_Tile.
